.sp
RSI (Resolvable Set Identifier) is used to advertise a resolvable identifier
for Coordinated Set Identification.
.INDENT 0.0
.TP
.B Usage
\fB> rsi [on/off]\fP
.TP
.B [on/off]
Enable or disable RSI advertisement (optional, shows current if omitted)
.TP
